      <title>特朗普特使和微笑的马杜罗重启委内瑞拉关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/trump-s-envoy-and-a-smiling-maduro-reset-venezuela-relations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一次旋风之旅中，唐纳德·特朗普总统的特使推翻了拜登政府多年来在委内瑞拉的外交政策，并与委内瑞拉总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗重新开始，这一转变可能会对从移民到石油市场产生影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/trump-s-envoy-and-a-smiling-maduro-reset-venezuela-relations</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 21:22:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大准备对特朗普关税采取报复措施，重新考虑对美国的依赖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/canada-poised-to-retaliate-against-trump-tariffs-while-rethinking-us-reliance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大即将出台升级的报复性反关税，试图让美国人反对唐纳德·特朗普总统对加拿大商品征收 25% 的关税，这一威胁促使美国重新考虑对南方邻国的依赖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/canada-poised-to-retaliate-against-trump-tariffs-while-rethinking-us-reliance</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 18:31:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
