    <item>
      <title>卢拉面临的挑战日益严峻，巴西国会选出新领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/brazil-s-congress-picks-new-leaders-as-lula-s-challenges-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦已经面临食品价格上涨、投资者怀疑情绪加深和支持率下降的问题。现在他又面临另一个挑战：国会领导层的变动将考验他驾驭该国保守立法机构的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/brazil-s-congress-picks-new-leaders-as-lula-s-challenges-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国公民在最新加沙人质囚犯交换行动中获释</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/fourth-hostage-prisoner-swap-underway-as-gaza-ceasefire-holds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[星期六早上，第四次人质与囚犯交换计划顺利进行，以色列和哈马斯遵守加沙停火第一阶段的协议，包括重新开放通往埃及的拉法口岸。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/fourth-hostage-prisoner-swap-underway-as-gaza-ceasefire-holds</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 07:44:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>根据最新交换协议，哈马斯将于周六释放三名男性人质</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-02-01/hamas-to-release-3-male-hostages-israel-to-release-dozens-of-palestinian-prisoners-under-ceasefire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汗尤尼斯，加沙地带（美联社）——周六，加沙停火协议实现了迄今为止最顺利的以色列人质与巴勒斯坦囚犯交换，而在停火协议难度大得多的第二阶段谈判开始前两天，至关重要的拉法边境口岸重新开放。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-02-01/hamas-to-release-3-male-hostages-israel-to-release-dozens-of-palestinian-prisoners-under-ceasefire</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 05:31:10 GMT</pubDate>
